Verisk Analytics to Buy Health Risk Partners for $60 Million

-- B y   B r o o k e   S u t h e r l a n d
-- 
2011-06-13T17:44:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-13/verisk-analytics-to-buy-health-risk-partners-for-60-million.html
Verisk Analytics Inc. (VRSK) , the supplier
of actuarial data to insurers and mortgage lenders, agreed to
buy Health Risk Partners LLC for $60 million in cash to add
sales to clients that serve Medicare and Medicaid patients.  Verisk will put $13 million of the purchase price in escrow
and the funds are expected to be paid in 2012, the  Jersey City ,
New Jersey-based company said today in a statement distributed
by Globe Newswire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brooke Sutherland in New York at 
 Bsutherland5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  